<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to DevV.me!</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8fafc;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center;">
        <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700;">🚀 Welcome to DevV.me!</h1>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9;">Your developer journey starts here</p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="padding: 40px 30px;">
        <div style="display: inline-block; background: #10b981; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px;">✨ Account Created Successfully</div>
        
        <h2 style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">Hi <%= @user.display_name %>!</h2>
        
        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Welcome to DevV.me! We're thrilled to have you join our community of developers. Your account has been created successfully and you're now part of our beta program.</p>
        
        <div style="background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #92400e; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600;">📋 Beta Access Status</h3>
          <p style="margin: 0;">Your account is currently <strong>pending activation</strong>. Our team will review and activate your account soon. You'll receive an email notification once your account is active and you have full access to all features.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p style="margin: 20px 0;">Once activated, you'll be able to:</p>
        
        <div style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0;">
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li style="margin: 8px 0;"><strong>Create and showcase your projects</strong> with rich descriptions and images</li>
            <li style="margin: 8px 0;"><strong>Write and publish blog posts</strong> with our markdown editor</li>
            <li style="margin: 8px 0;"><strong>Build your developer profile</strong> with your skills and experience</li>
            <li style="margin: 8px 0;"><strong>Share your profile</strong> with the unique URL: <strong>devv.me/<%= @user.username %></strong></li>
            <li style="margin: 8px 0;"><strong>Connect with other developers</strong> in our growing community</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
          <a href="<%= @dashboard_url %>" style="display: inline-block; background: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 10px;">Go to Dashboard</a>
          <a href="<%= @profile_url %>" style="display: inline-block; background: #6b7280; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 10px;">View Your Profile</a>
        </div>
        
        <p style="margin: 20px 0;">In the meantime, feel free to explore the platform and get familiar with the interface. As a beta user, your feedback is incredibly valuable to us!</p>
        
        <p style="margin: 20px 0;">If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
        
        <p style="margin: 20px 0;">Welcome to the community!</p>
        
        <p style="margin: 20px 0;">Best regards,<br>The DevV.me Team</p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px 30px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">
        <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">You're receiving this email because you created a DevV.me account.</p>
        <p style="margin: 0;">If you have any questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@devv.me" style="color: #3b82f6; text-decoration: none;">support@devv.me</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
